metadata.name: World Of Pandas #1
metadata.description: In the Rough Metaverse, 8008 Pandas, with 8 of them being the 'Gods' are thrown into complete chaos representing and living a different lifestyle, Casualties of everyday challenges and difficulties are there to survive and get to the top by facing the hardness of the real life. With our Panda's Uniqueness and our Panda's World, we are UNITING to achieve our dreams.
